  "name": "Shimmerstone staff, sunset",
  "type": "weapon",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Shimmerstone is a unique mineral found only in the frozen mountains of Vesk-8. A deep, translucent blue, it is reminiscent of thick ice in its raw form, and it glitters with a three-dimensional field comprised of tiny points of light. Kothamas have long fashioned small amounts of the mineral&mdash;relative to their large scale&mdash;into foci, contemplating the glittering objects during the day or when there is inclement weather as a substitute for the starry night sky.</p>\n<p>Vesk forces, upon first encountering this mineral, noted its calming effect and immediately set to work developing military applications, eventually fashioning it into supplementary weapons for spellcasters.</p>\n<p>A shimmerstone staff is a hybrid item that functions as a two-handed advanced melee weapon. While you are wielding a shimmerstone staff, the DCs of your charm and emotion spells and effects are increased by 1.</p>",
